// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-5414 — Mass File Rename (medusalocker)
// Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 44bbabce-2619-5bb9-ad09-53ca19a97d51

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
